item.title: 39 Maharashtra Ministers Join Devendra Fadnavis' Cabinet. Full List - NDTV
item.description:
39 Maharashtra Ministers Join Devendra Fadnavis' Cabinet. Full List

The much-awaited cabinet expansion of the new Maharashtra government led by Chief Minister Devendra Fadnavis happened today, with 39 ministers taking oath.

  • 19 ministers from BJP
  • 9 ministers from NCP
  • 11 ministers from Shiv Sena
  • Cabinet expansion took place in Nagpur

Conclusion: A significant cabinet expansion marks the new government's composition in Maharashtra.

item.title: Delhi polls: AAP unveils 38 candidates, Kejriwal to contest from New Delhi| Full list - Hindustan Times
item.description:
Delhi Assembly Elections: AAP Announces 38 Candidates Including Kejriwal

  • AAP reveals its final list of 38 candidates for the 2025 Delhi Elections.
  • Arvind Kejriwal contests from New Delhi against Sandeep Dikshit.
  • Atishi, Saurabh Bharadwaj, and Gopal Rai are also key candidates.
  • Seventeen current lawmakers have been removed from AAP's lists so far.

Conclusion: The AAP is determined to secure another term in Delhi with a comprehensive list of candidates.
